name: Animals #1 Cows
description:
Cow pics made with Panasonic FZ82 with Impressive Art filter on. Used about 7 in that clip, duplicated etc.
Merged them together in simple video editor, created a sound loop on my DJ gear using 2 sound files, cows and chill out sample.
Combined both files in PhotoMosh Pro, enabled few filters, some sound active, some not :)
Enjoy!
